			<category name="Description">
				<comment>By Aaron0000</comment>
				<comment>Gives all the standard guns, shields, and grenades some new coats of paint. Enable what you want with the Community Mod Manager, they're all off by default.</comment>
				<comment>General themeing for the items (from common to very rare when listed);</comment>
				<comment>Bandit - From crappier wooden, homemade guns to metal, thuggish guns.</comment>
				<comment>Dahl - Camos for regions. (Southern) Shelf Camo, Dust Camo, Highland Camo, Eridium Camo.</comment>
				<comment>Hyperion - Valuable metals (also gains a stripe for each rarity). Copper, Bronze, Silver, Gold.</comment>
				<comment>Jakobs - Based on Old West firearms.</comment>
				<comment>Maliwan - Artistic-ish. Also color coordinates with rarity.</comment>
				<comment>Tediore - Matches rarity color.</comment>
				<comment>Torgue - Something vaguely hot rod-ish.</comment>
				<comment>Vladof - Based on Soviet firearms.</comment>
				<comment>Anshin - Matches with color of rarity (excluding Very Rare), gains first aid signs at Very Rare.</comment>
				<comment>Pangolin - Wood/Iron, Steel, Carbon, Diamond.</comment>
			</category>
